"This directory is a SSD drive with fast read-write access and up to 50 ‚Äì¬†"
"100 GBs of disk space. Ideal use cases for `/tmp` are for processing "
"large datasets that do not need to be stored permanently."
msgstr ""

msgid "Cloud Object Storage"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Your hub lives in the cloud, therefore another way to store data is using"
" object storage such as Amazon S3 or Google Cloud Storage. This type of "
"storage is ideally suited for persistent, large datasets that would be "
"otherwise expensive to store on a traditional filesystem (i.e. your home,"
" shared or `/tmp` folder) long-term."
msgstr ""

