"GitHub App, provide a public URL of the GitHub App and update the hub "
"configuration to make the `GH_SCOPED_CREDS_CLIENT_ID` and "
"`GH_SCOPED_CREDS_APP_URL` environment variables available in your hub."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Check that the GitHub App is installed to your GitHub Organization/GitHub"
" personal account that owns the repositories you would like access to."
msgstr ""

