"**GitHub Organization:** Navigate to the GitHub Organization used to "
"manage access to your hub. In this lesson we are using the [2i2c-"
"community-showcase](https://github.com/2i2c-community-showcase) GitHub "
"Organization to manage access to the Community Showcase Hub."
